Class BobberBike

  • java.lang.Object
    • Bootcamps.Bootcamp05.edu.monash.fit2099.vehicles.Vehicle
      • Bootcamps.Bootcamp05.edu.monash.fit2099.vehicles.BobberBike

  • public class BobberBike
extends Vehicle
    The BobberBike class handles the creation, characteristics and behaviour of all bobber bikes present in the car auction. It represents a generic bobber bike, and extends the vehicle class as it a type of vehicle. This is version 5 of this class, as it is from Week 5's Bootcamp.
